    size: 'XL',
    breed: 'Labrador Retriever',
    name: 'Roger',
    sex: 'Male',
    description: 'Roger came to the shelter as a stray, nervous and uncomfortable with being handled or walked. Today, this sweet boy is a big goof who loves prancing around on walks, running after toys, playing fetch and sitting down for a good scratch from his new human friends. All to say that Roger has come a long way! And he\'s ready to take his next trot into his new life in a new forever home. He\'s a easygoing, adventurous boy who walks well on his leash. He\'s answering to the sit, down, place and beg commands and is working on shake and drop. And he\'s doing well in playgroup with his new doggie friends. A house with a yard to play in and humans to give him the affection he loves would be ideal for Roger. Come visit and see if he\'s perfect for your home.',
