    size: 'XL',
    breed: 'Pit Bull Terrier',
    name: 'Moose',
    sex: 'Male',
    description: 'In a word, Moose is magnificent! Just look at him and you\'ll see he\'s a sight to behold. This big lug of a dog has captured the hearts of many ladies here at the shelter. With his movie star good looks and strong, silent demeanor, it\'s easy to see how he became such a heartthrob! Good looks aside, Moose has so much to offer. Like James Dean, he\'s a bit of shy guy, but it won\'t take long for him to warm up and nuzzle you with that jowly face. He appears to be a serious dude in the kennel, but he morphs into a puppy when he\'s chasing his toys or taking a dip in the pool. His two passions in life are fetch and swimming. So if you\'re looking for an athletic, fun-loving guy, Moose is it! If you\'re a lover of the great outdoors, Moose is your perfect fit. He is a great walking and running companion. He goes out with his Virtual Foster friend every night for evening walks around the ball field. He\'s a gentleman on the leash and is learning some new skills. He\'s eager to please and will work hard for treats! Also, we should note that he appears to be potty trained and could potentially live in a home with a well-matched pup. So what do you say? Why not stop by APA today and see for yourself how much our Magnificent Moose has to offer? If you can look past his shyness, you\'ll see how much fun you both could have together!',
