    name: 'Rilo',
    sex: 'Female',
    description: 'Independent, Goofy, Hefty Want a cat that will make you laugh? Then Rilo is your gal! This chunky lady is a hoot, and she will make you chuckle to watch her chase her toys around. Rilo loves to watch the birds fly by the window and will take naps in the sunbeams. She also loves to eat (if you couldn\'t tell). She is a polite house guest and always goes in her litter box; she knows that lady cats must have good bathroom manners! Rilo isn\'t too much of a fan of other cats, but doesn\'t mind being around cats that respect her space. She can get over-stimulated during play, so we recommend a home with older children. If you want a goofy, playful, and independent companion, then Rilo is the perfect cat for you! All APA! cats and kittens are fully vetted, spayed or neutered, and have updated vaccines and a microchip. Lifetime support is offered by our Cat Behavior Team.?? For further information or to meet Rilo, please emailadopt@austinpetsalive.org.',
