    name: 'Sophia',
    sex: 'Female',
    description: 'Quiet, Affectionate, Lovely Sophia\'s gorgeous coat is a mixture of tabby orange, pure white and flourishes of black with a beauty mark that\'s to die for...no wonder she\'s the envy of all the kitties! But, Sophia\'s good looks have not gone to her head. She\'s such a sweetheart who longs for a sense of security and a warm, welcoming lap! Sophia is a bit shy with new people. But, give her a little time to get to know you and you\'ll see the uncertainty in those lovely green eyes change to adoration and trust. Then it\'s time to bring on the head scratches and to get ready for cozy times with this gentle angel happily snuggling by your side! Sophia has made efforts to make friends other cats at the shelter, so she would likely enjoy a kitty companion. No need to fret over what to feed her at meal time. Sophia keeps it simple! She needs to be on a special diet of Hill\'s C/D which is carried at local pet stores and is available online. Sophia is an all-around mellow kitty who dreams of the comfort a calm home and a loving human would surely bring. If you can imagine this lovely lady curled up beside you and warming your heart each and every day, come meet Sophia today! All APA! cats are fully vetted, spayed or neutered, and have updated vaccines and a microchip. Lifetime support is offered by our Cat Behavior Team. For further information or to meet Sophia, please email adopt@austinpetsalive.org.',
