    size: 'XL',
    breed: { '$t': 'Labrador Retriever' },
    name: 'Timmy',
    sex: 'Male',
    description: 'We don\'t know much about Timmy\'s past, but we know he\'s been through a lot. His tail is always wagging, and he looks at our volunteers with so much hope and love. But there\'s something holding him back from trusting 100%. He is a dog in need of real rescuing, and we\'re hoping there is a special person out there who can show him there\'s good things in store. Timmy loves to go on walks and is a great leash walker. He doesn\'t really like to be petted, but once he trusts you, he will sometimes lay his head in your lap and gaze at you adoringly. He doesn\'t do that with just anyone, so if you get The Look, you know you\'ve earned a special place in his heart. It might take some time to really forge a bond with Timmy, but once you do, we know it will be a friendship that you will never forget. Timmy is exactly the kind of dog APA! is here for. If you have room in your life to help a lost soul who really needs it, consider Timmy.',
