    size: 'L',
    breed: 'Pit Bull Terrier',
    name: 'Lamar',
    sex: 'Male',
    description: 'Though Lamar will play and enjoys some play time, he\'s really all about affection and being close to those he loves. He does enjoy his walks and is great on his leash. When at playgroup, he cavorts for a little while, but then he\'s quite content to find his special friend or friends and settle in for some snuggle time. Apparently Lamar is a great kitchen companion. He\'s not opposed to trying new things, any or all, and is happy to clean up any kitchen mess made during this new recipe try out fun. And the look in his happy eyes will let you know, you\'ve found a winner of a new recipe. Lamar would be happiest in a home with adults or older children who understand the best relationships develop a little slowly then becoming enduring and strong. He might enjoy one doggy friend in the house as well. This boy is one happy go lucky and super affectionate guy. When he gets one-on-one time with his friends at the shelter, his tail won\'t stop wagging and he makes it known how grateful he is for attention and affection. This guy deserves his very own all the time snuggle partner/s. Come meet him and start that process of getting to know him as soon as you can get here. He\'s waiting to meet you and start that tail wagging just for you.',
